{"type":"question","id":18186,"title":"为什么网易新闻能一直有大量敏感的评论存在？","uid":32217,"topics":[3365,1547],"contents":"小弟以前是混网易的，海外只知道有大纪元，后来才知道有品葱膜乎这些专业的海外流亡论坛。我一直觉得网易新闻非常好，敢打擦边球，而且居然一直敢在评论上保留大量讽刺色情言论：只要你不是直接喊共产党滚蛋吧，而是以比喻或讽刺的方法表达出来，那大概率不会被删帖（直接在中央领导人和外交部新闻底下回复的评论除外）。我一直觉得很奇怪，难道丁磊有什么特殊背景，能让网易新闻变得如此“有态度”？而不会沦为新浪搜狐腾讯那样一片粉红？<br>\n<br>\n底下是我最近看的网易新闻和评论，可见从编辑到回帖的网友都比较“反动”<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/S3aOrrI.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/S3aOrrI.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/S3aOrrI.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z11mEBp.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z11mEBp.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z11mEBp.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/mgYuqWT.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mgYuqWT.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mgYuqWT.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/TGV7laI.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TGV7laI.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/TGV7laI.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/zLNqExV.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zLNqExV.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zLNqExV.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/d1Di0o9.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d1Di0o9.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/d1Di0o9.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IhzXKDb.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IhzXKDb.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/IhzXKDb.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-02-12","agreeCount":17,"discussionCount":9}